name: spleeter-gpu
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "spleeter-gpu" %}
{% set version = "1.5.3" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  - url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: dc9c6f2a4f092c93565368c66ba2efa7c2ac82e0cc698a8f3ec8c4f6ff7714ee

build:
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  noarch: python
  entry_points:
    - spleeter = spleeter.__main__:entrypoint

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6,<3.8
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6,<3.8
    - requests
    - setuptools
    - importlib_resources
    - tensorflow-gpu ==1.14.0
    - pandas ==0.25.1
    - ffmpeg-python
    - norbert

test:
  imports:
    - spleeter

about:
  home: https://github.com/deezer/spleeter
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: The Deezer source separation library with pretrained models based on tensorflow.
  doc_url: https://github.com/deezer/spleeter/wiki
  dev_url: https://github.com/deezer/spleeter

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - Faylixe
    - romi1502
